        {
            "title": "橋水聯合基金首席投資官稱人工智能對軟件公司構成生存威脅",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DkDpYjpDmIaIJWpMGtgkUQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA8400B_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 橋水聯合基金(Bridgewater Associates)週一表示,<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"人工智能\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:人工智能;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/人工智能\">人工智能</a>對傳統軟件公司構成生存威脅,這與1990年代亞馬遜顛覆傳統書店的情況如出一轍。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該投資公司的聯席首席投資官鮑勃·普林斯(Bob Prince)、格雷格·詹森(Greg Jensen)和卡倫·卡尼奧爾-坦布爾(Karen Karniol-Tambour)在一份客戶報告中寫道,最新發布的Claude Code對大型企業構成了重大風險,類似於幾十年前亞馬遜對巴諾書店(Barnes &amp; Noble)構成的挑戰。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-63b04ca0-7319-3081-81a0-de4fdeaec8f6-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一警告正值軟件股面臨巨大拋售壓力之際。標普500軟件與服務指數今年已下跌16.6%,市場擔憂新發布的人工智能模型可能顛覆傳統軟件公司。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">企業軟件、客戶關係管理和創意設計公司受到的影響尤為嚴重。Salesforce今年迄今下跌33%,Adobe下跌30%,ServiceNow下跌41%,Intuit下跌37.5%,HubSpot下跌39%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">橋水聯合基金的高管們寫道:\"市場已開始將應用軟件公司面臨的風險納入定價,企業要麼與人工智能共同進化,要麼面臨顛覆。\"</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">從大型科技公司到金融服務業,各板塊的裁員正在增加,企業削減數千個職位並將原因歸咎於人工智能部署帶來的成本節約。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">橋水聯合基金還警告稱,持續的地緣政治動盪將繼續擾亂市場和大宗商品。該公司表示,美國在委內瑞拉、格陵蘭和伊朗的行動可能加速美國主導的聯盟體系出現裂痕。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">通過霍爾木茲海峽的航運仍然低迷,該海峽處理全球約五分之一的能源流動,而伊朗的緩和努力陷入停滯。這場衝突導致大宗商品短缺並引發通脹擔憂。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該報告稱:\"大宗商品衝擊將持續一段時間。\"</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%A9%8B%E6%B0%B4%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E9%A6%96%E5%B8%AD%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E5%AE%98%E7%A8%B1%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%A5%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E5%B0%8D%E8%BB%9F%E4%BB%B6%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%A7%8B%E6%88%90%E7%94%9F%E5%AD%98%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85-161006134.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-28 00:32:13",
